{
  "name": "lvngErly_page",
  "elements": [
    {
      "type": "panel",
      "name": "lvngErlyPanel",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "html",
          "name": "lvngErlyHeading",
          "html": "<h3>Your early encounters with laryngeal paralysis (LP)</h3>"
        },
        {
          "type": "html",
          "name": "lvngErlyText",
          "html": "<p>Most people know something's wrong with their companion before they know it's LP or even before they know there is such a thing as LP. This section asks questions about the early phase of your LP journey and how you came to accept that {lndgRootCmpnName} might have it.</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "lvngErlyFirstSignsPanel",
          "title": "About how old was {lndgRootCmpnName} (in years and months) when you first noticed signs of what you later learned was LP?",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "inputType": "number",
              "name": "lvngErlyFirstSignsAgeYears",
              "title": "Years",
              "isRequired": true,
              "min": "1",
              "max": "40",
                "validators": [
                {
                  "type": "numeric",
                  "minValue": 1,
                  "maxValue": 40,
                  "text": "Age must be between 1 and 40"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "inputType": "number",
              "name": "lvngErlyFirstSignsAgeMonths",
              "title": "Months (number 1 - 12)",
              "isRequired": true,
              "min": 1,
              "max": 12,
              "validators": [
                {
                  "type": "numeric",
                  "minValue": 1,
                  "maxValue": 12,
                  "text": "Months must be between 1 and 12"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "lvngErlySymptomsPanel",
          "elements": [
            {
              "type": "checkbox",
              "name": "lvngErlySymptoms",
              "title": "What symptoms did {lndgRootCmpnName} have at that time?",
              "choices": [
                {
                  "value": "Noisy Breathing",
                  "text": "Noisy or raspy breathing"
                },
                {
                  "value": "Excess panting",
                  "text": "Excess panting"
                },
                {
                  "value": "Changes in bark",
                  "text": "Changes in bark"
                },
                {
                  "value": "Coughing or hacking",
                  "text": "Coughing or hacking"
                },
                {
                  "value": "Gagging or retching",
                  "text": "Gagging or retching"
                },
                {
                  "value": "Labored breathing",
                  "text": "Labored Breathing"
                },
                {
                  "value": "Exercise and heat intolerance",
                  "text": "Exercise and heat intolerance"
                },
                {
                  "value": "Tongue turning blue",
                  "text": "Tongue or gums turning blue"
                },
                {
                  "value": "Syncope",
                  "text": "Syncope (passing out)"
                }
              ],
              "showOtherItem": true,
              "showNoneItem": true,
              "noneText": "Don't know",
              "otherText": "Other (please describe)"
            },
            {
              "type": "rating",
              "name": "lvngErlySymptomSeverity",
              "title": "How severe did you think {lndgRootCmpnName}'s early symptoms were?",
              "description": "1 = mild, 5 = severe",
              "isRequired": true
            },
            {
              "type": "radiogroup",
              "name": "lvngErlyHindEndWeakness",
              "title": "Was {lndgRootCmpnName} already showing signs of hind-end weakness in this early stage?",
              "choices": [
                "Yes",
                "No",
                "Don't remember"
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "panel",
          "name": "lvngErlyOtherConditions",
          "elements": [
            {
            "type": "checkbox",
            "name": "lvngErlyOtherConditions",
            "title": "Which other conditions did {lndgRootCmpnName} have when the first LP symptoms appeared?",
            "required": true,
            "choices": [
                {
                  "value": "Acid reflux",
                  "text": "Acid reflux (GERD)"
                },
                {
                  "value": "Megaesophagus",
                  "text": "Megaesophagus"
                },
                {
                  "value": "Periodontal disease",
                  "text": "Periodontal disease"
                }
              ],
              "choicesOrder": "none",
              "otherText": "Other",
              "showOtherItem": true
            },
            {
              "type": "radiogroup",
              "name": "lvngErlyIntubated",
              "title": "Had {lndgRootCmpnName} been intubated under anesthesia for any reason in the 12 months prior to the first LP symptoms?",
              "choices": [
                "Yes",
                "No",
                "Don't remember"
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "radiogroup",
              "name": "lvngErlyIntubatedReason",
              "title": "For what reason was {lndgRootCmpnName} intubated prior to the first LP symptoms appearing?",
              "choices": [
                  {
                    "value": "Teeth cleaning",
                    "text": "Teeth cleaning"
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "Dental surgery",
                    "text": "Dental surgery"
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "Non-dental surgery",
                    "text": "Non-dental surgery"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "Diagnostic procedure",
                    "value": "Diagnostic procedure"
                  },
                                    {
                    "text": "Emergency procedure",
                    "value": "Emergency procedure"
                  }
                ],
                "choicesOrder": "none",
                "otherText": "Other",
                "showOtherItem": true
            },
            {
              "type": "radiogroup",
              "name": "lvngErlyIntubatedFacility",
              "title": "In what type of facility was {lndgRootCmpnName}'s intubation/anesthesia carried out?",
              "choices": [
                  {
                    "value": "Primary veterinarian",
                    "text": "Primary veterinarian"
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "Independent specialist",
                    "text": "Specialist at independent veterinary clinic/hospital"
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "Teaching college",
                    "text": "Private or state-affiliated teaching college or institution"
                  },
                  {
                    "value": "Emergency veterinarian",
                    "text": "Emergency veterinary clinic or hospital"
                  },
                                    {
                    "value": "Don't remember",
                    "text": "Don't remember"
                  }
              ],
              "choicesOrder": "none",
              "otherText": "Other",
              "showOtherItem": true
            },
            {
              "type": "boolean",
              "name": "lvngErlyIntubationConcerns",
              "title": "Do you remember having any concerns about how the intubation/anesthesia affected {lndgRootCmpnName}?",
              "isRequired": true
            },
            {
              "type": "checkbox",
              "name": "lvngErlyIntubationSymptoms",
              "title": "What symptoms did {lndgRootCmpnName} have after the intubation/anesthesia?",
              "choices": [
                {
                  "value": "Coughing and hacking",
                  "text": "Coughing and hacking"
                },
                {
                  "value": "Gagging and retching",
                  "text": "Gagging and retching"
                },
                {
                  "value": "Difficulty breathing",
                  "text": "Difficulty breathing"
                },
                {
                  "value": "Altered mental state",
                  "text": "Altered mental state"
                }
              ],
              "choicesOrder": "none",
              "otherText": "Other",
              "visibleIf": "{lvngErlyIntubationConcerns} = 'true'",
              "showOtherItem": true
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}